Merge pull request #4989 from openshift-cherrypick-robot/cherry-pick-4984-to-release-1.31

[release-1.31] [CI:BUILD] rpm: spdx compatible license field

rpm: spdx compatible license field

The lowercase `and` in the License field isn't compatible with spdx
license format.

This commit replaces all `and` with `AND` in the License field in spec.

[NO NEW TESTS NEEDED]
